HEADWORD: Prefigure
<hw>Pre*fig"ure</hw> <pr>(?; 135)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Prefigured</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>;
<pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos> <conjf>Prefiguring</conjf>.]</vmorph>
<ety>[F. <ets>pr⟦eacute⟧figurer</ets>, or L. <ets>praefigurare</ets>,
